{{Character info |crawler_#=12,330,800 |age=99 |class= [[Blizzardmancer]] -> [[Tundra Princess]] |species=Human {{!}} [[Frost Maiden]] |origin=Wenatchee, Washington |occupation=[[Meadow Lark]] Patient |first_appearance=Chapter 37 |status=Alive |party=[[Meadow Lark]] |allies= *[[Imani C]] *[[Chris Andrews]] *[[Carl]] *[[Donut]] |gear= |level=72|image1=[[File:Elle frost maiden.png|220px|center|thumb|alt=Elle|AI-generated]]|height=4'6"}}
Elle McGibbons was a patient at [[Meadow Lark]] before entering the dungeon. She is one of the elderly people who is sheparded to the [[Third Floor|Third Floor]] of [[Dungeon|The Dungeon]] by [[Imani C]], [[Brandon An]], [[Chris Andrews|Chris Andrews 2]], [[Carl]], and [[Donut]]. Her husband was named Barry.
Upon reaching the third floor, she chooses a race that allows her to recover from the mental and physical degradation of her extreme age, that also comes with the Manager benefit. Her manager is [[Mistress Tiatha]].
== Description ==
After she turns into a [[Frost Maiden]], she appears to be an elf with blue skin and white hair. She floats instead of walking. She is four and a half feet tall and still wears her Meadow Lark anti-slip socks.
== Appearance == She wears s simple gold wedding ring around her neck like a chain and anti slip socks.
== Personality == She is a firecracker. Besides cursing like a sailor, she flirts with [[Carl]] in an overtly sexual manner. She's also a stone cold killer, showing no remorse when killing, seemingly because she sees it as unavoidable and therefore unworthy of regret.
== Gear == {{Spoiler | book = 6 | spoiler = After hitting the 8th floor she received a powerful ice staff. }}
== Powers == {{Spoiler | book = 5 | spoiler = She is part earth, part water-mage and on the “4 seasons path” according to Samantha. }} {{Spoiler | book = 6 | spoiler = Rose 6 levels to level 72 at the end of book 6 from casting a single spell, killing a lot of demons. }}
