{{citation}}
An addictive species specific opioid produced by the Krakaren. Used to keep the mobs of the [[Fourth Floor|Iron Tangle]] in order.

One of the side effects of the Rev-Up Vitamin Shot is the possibility of addiction, if customers get addicted and fail to get their shot they start experiencing the effects of withdraw, if not treated in time they begin to suffer from a dreaded condition known as the DTs.

'''Stage one''' – suffers are overcome with violent terror, their mind starting to rot out from within, only 50% of suffers survive this stag, half move on to stag two which allows for increased mobility, the other half die transforming into a festering ghoul. Festering ghouls have two objects, to devour as much organic material as possible and find more of their kind.
