{{Character_info|species=[[Bopca Protector]]|titles=Caretaker|first_appearance=Chapter 9|level=63}}
Tally is the first Bopca Protector encountered by Carl and Donut. He is described by Carl as a furry creature, barely taller than the counter, with brown hair with an odd greenish tinge. His face is quite hairy, such that Carl can only see his black eyes and veiny bulbous nose. He complains about the crawl opening early, but seems pleased to be asked to make what he would like for Carl to eat.
He tells Carl that when the first floor collapses, he will move to a random floor until he is no longer needed, and advises them to purchase accessories for their personal spaces as soon as they can. [[Category:Characters]] [[Category:NPC]]

