The '''Zulu Warrior''' is a class available on the [[Third Floor|third floor]]. It was picked by [[Chris Andrews|Chris Andrews 2]].<ref>{{ref|4|14}}</ref> 

== Speculation ==
It seems very likely that this is an Earth Class. It may be a Fighter subclass inspired by the impi/tribal zulu warriors, who were known to wield spears and shields.<ref>"Impi." ''Wikipedia''. [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impi#:~:text=In%20English%20impi%20is%20often,in%20Zulu%20or%20the%20army. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Impi#:~:text=In%20English%20impi%20is%20often,in%20Zulu%20or%20the%20army.]</ref>  [[Chris Andrews|Chris Andrews 2]] received an enchanted spear on the first floor,<ref>Dinniman, Matt. ''Dungeon Crawler Carl'' (chapter 26).</ref> and - as a [[cretin]] - is essentially a walking shield.

{{Spoiler
| book = 4
| spoiler = It's possible that it could also be a Mage subclass as [[Vadim]] claimed that [[Chris Andrews|Chris]] had a lot of spells.<ref>{{ref|4|25}}</ref> 
Of coursem these may have been [[Maggie My|Maggie's]] spells.
}}

